.DT
register
Discworld player help
register

.SH Name
.SI 5
register - Register one of your other characters as an alt.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
register <alt>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command will officially record another character as owned by you.
You will have to enter the password for your current character, and
your alt before the registration will be performed.

Forgotten passwords, or stolen characters, can be returned to their
rightful owner if they are registered as alts of their rightful owner.
.EP

.SH See also
.SI 5
password
.EI
